{"id":276312,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/global-voices-乌兹别克斯坦：毫无用处的拉丁字母/","date":"2013-01-26T12:00:20Z","modified":"2013-01-26T12:00:20Z","title":"Global Voices | 乌兹别克斯坦：毫无用处的拉丁字母","content":"<p><p>LiveJournal用户a_volosevich<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://a-volosevich.livejournal.com/29317.html\">认为</a>俄，乌兹别克斯坦过去二十年来进行的字母拉丁化改革，正面临失败。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>新的书写字母并没有创造外语知识，乌兹别克斯坦改用拉丁字母近二十年来，这已成为不争的事实。……除此之外，相较于拉丁化后的乌兹别克斯坦语，俄语的需求量更大。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这位博客认为，对哈萨克斯坦来说这可能会是个警讯。哈萨克斯坦也正准备<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/12/19/kazakhstan-to-switch-to-latin-script/\">停用</a>西里尔字母，改用拉丁字母。</p>\n<div>校对者：Soup</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/alexander-sodiqov/\" title=\"文章导读 Alexander Sodiqov\">Alexander Sodiqov</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/01/24/uzbekistans-useless-latin-script/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/01/26/12148/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%B9%E5%88%AB%E5%85%8B%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%AF%AB%E6%97%A0%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%84%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F01%2F26%2F12148%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F01%2F26%2F12148%2F&#038;desc=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%B9%E5%88%AB%E5%85%8B%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%AF%AB%E6%97%A0%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%84%E7%9A%84%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%81%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D\" title=\"MyShare\"><sp